The title and abstract specifically mention "multidimensional binary search," which is a topic in data structures and algorithms, hence cs.DS is a likely category. However, the focus on game-theoretic applications and learning algorithms suggests that cs.GT and cs.LG are more likely categories. Finally, the mention of "high-dimensional geometry" and "convex analysis" suggests that cs.IT may also be a relevant category.
